If you're not local your best bet is to donate. The best people to work the ground game are the people that live there. I wanted to help to, so I donated.  


If you still want to volunteer, check out [https://fairfight.com/join-our-fight/](https://fairfight.com/join-our-fight/)
Can we stop pretending like the stock market matters to most people, or that it's representative of the economy. Thanks in advance!
